the Nipah virus.

126
00:10:00,808 --> 00:10:03,144
But how is he going to prove that?

127
00:10:04,395 --> 00:10:06,480
The fact is that we currently have
a suspected patient.

128
00:10:06,564 --> 00:10:09,942
Don't make any rash decisions
until we get the results.

129
00:10:10,026 --> 00:10:13,112
Regardless of the result,
Dr. Cha entered the center

130
00:10:13,821 --> 00:10:15,531
and he must be punished for it.

131
00:10:26,667 --> 00:10:29,879
I've been thinking this for a while.
You're really bad at drawing.

132
00:10:56,947 --> 00:10:59,158
Don't take off
any of your protection equipment

133
00:11:00,534 --> 00:11:02,244
until you get out of here.

134
