if I tell you to.

136
00:11:12,254 --> 00:11:14,840
And you're obviously not
going to stay still either.

137
00:11:14,924 --> 00:11:16,217
-It'll be a waste of energy.

138
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:17,968
You shouldn't have fallen down.

139
00:11:23,057 --> 00:11:24,809
-Dr. Lee.
-Yes?

140
00:11:28,854 --> 00:11:30,398
I want you guys to concentrate.

141
